@host = http://localhost:5100

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Register
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "player@example.com",
  "password": "ClassicWow1",
  "displayName": "Azeroth Explorer"
}

### Login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "player@example.com",
  "password": "ClassicWow1",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### Current user (send the wowiki.auth cookie returned by register/login)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me

### Logout
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout
